<div class="nass margin-top-10"> <p><span id="p1" class="anchor"></span><span class="c2">(١١)</span> ... <span class="c3">{وَأَحْيَيْتَنَا اثْنَتَيْنِ}</span> ... مَرَّةً فيِ الدُّنْيَا، وَمَرَّةً فيِ الآخِرَةِ.<a href="#p1" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p2"></span><span class="c2">(١١)</span> ... <span class="c3">{سَبِيلٍ}</span> ... طَرِيقٍ نَخْرُجُ بِهِ مِنَ النَّارِ.<a href="#p2" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p3"></span><span class="c2">(١٣)</span> ... <span class="c3">{رِزْقًا}</span> ... مَطَرًا تُرْزَقُونَ بِهِ.<a href="#p3" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p4"></span><span class="c2">(١٣)</span> ... <span class="c3">{يُنِيبُ}</span> ... يَرْجِعُ إِلَى طَاعَةِ اللهِ.<a href="#p4" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p5"></span><span class="c2">(١٥)</span> ... <span class="c3">{رَفِيعُ الدَّرَجَاتِ}</span> ... ارْتَفَعَتْ دَرَجَاتُهُ ارْتِفَاعًا بَايَنَ بِهِ مَخْلُوقَاتِهِ، وَارْتَفَعَ بِهِ قَدْرُهُ.<a href="#p5" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p6"></span><span class="c2">(١٥)</span> ... <span class="c3">{يُلْقِي الرُّوحَ}</span> ... يُنْزِلُ الوَحْيَ.<a href="#p6" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p7"></span><span class="c2">(١٥)</span> ... <span class="c3">{يَوْمَ التَّلَاقِ}</span> ... اليَوْمَ الَّذِي يَلْتَقِي فِيهِ الأَوَّلُونَ وَالآخِرُونَ.<a href="#p7" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p8"></span><span class="c2">(١٦)</span> ... <span class="c3">{بَارِزُونَ}</span> ... ظَاهِرُونَ أَمَامَ رَبِّهِمْ.<a href="#p8" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p9"></span><span class="c2">(١٨)</span> ... <span class="c3">{يَوْمَ الْآزِفَةِ}</span> ... يَوْمَ القِيَامَةِ القَرِيبَ.<a href="#p9" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p10"></span><span class="c2">(١٨)</span> ... <span class="c3">{لَدَى الْحَنَاجِرِ}</span> ... قُلُوبُهُمْ عِنْدَ حُلُوقِهِمْ مِنْ شِدَّةِ الكَرْبِ.<a href="#p10" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p11"></span><span class="c2">(١٨)</span> ... <span class="c3">{كَاظِمِينَ}</span> ... مُمْتَلِئِينَ غَمًّا، وَحُزْنًا.<a href="#p11" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p12"></span><span class="c2">(١٨)</span> ... <span class="c3">{حَمِيمٍ}</span> ... قَرِيبٍ، وَصَاحِبٍ.<a href="#p12" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p13"></span><span class="c2">(١٩)</span> ... <span class="c3">{خَائِنَةَ الْأَعْيُنِ}</span> ... مَا تَخْتَلِسُهُ العُيُونُ مِنَ النَّظَرِ إِلَى مَا لَا يَحِلُّ.<a href="#p13" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p14"></span><span class="c2">(٢٠)</span> ... <span class="c3">{يَقْضِي بِالْحَقِّ}</span> ... يَحْكُمُ بِالعَدْلِ.<a href="#p14" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p15"></span><span class="c2">(٢١)</span> ... <span class="c3">{وَاقٍ}</span> ... دَافِعٍ.<a href="#p15" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p16"></span><span class="c2">(٢٣)</span> ... <span class="c3">{وَسُلْطَانٍ مُّبِينٍ}</span> ... حُجَّةٍ بَيِّنَةٍ عَلَى صِدْقِهِ.<a href="#p16" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p> </div>